{
  "id": "5ae804a9665d8600148ce0dd",
  "title": "コミュニティ・クラッシャー",
  "created": 1525154989,
  "updated": 1525160974,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5ae804a9665d8600148ce0dd",
      "text": "コミュニティ・クラッシャー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525154989,
      "updated": 1525154991
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae8082faff09e00002334f1",
      "text": "クラッシャーが[コミュニティ]を壊す過程で何が行われているかに関する良い分析",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155887,
      "updated": 1525160970
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae804afaff09e00002334c6",
      "text": " [本当に怖い「コミュニティ・クラッシャー」の存在　ゆがんだ承認欲求の持ち主が、ウソの陰口でリーダーの足を引っ張る | キャリコネニュース https://news.careerconnection.jp/?p=24425]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525154991,
      "updated": 1525155890
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae804c1aff09e00002334c7",
      "text": " [曽和 利光]の「[働きやすい職場]とは何か」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155009,
      "updated": 1525160974
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae8056baff09e00002334cd",
      "text": " 著者は人事コンサルタント [曽和利光 - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9B%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%88%A9%E5%85%89]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155179,
      "updated": 1525155892
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae807efaff09e00002334ed",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155823,
      "updated": 1525155823
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae8057aaff09e00002334d0",
      "text": "クラッシャーが行うこと",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155194,
      "updated": 1525155826
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae8053aaff09e00002334cc",
      "text": "\t1: リーダー・主要メンバーの陰口を言う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155130,
      "updated": 1525155220
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae80594aff09e00002334d2",
      "text": " \t繰り返すうちに「火のないところに煙は出ない」となる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155220,
      "updated": 1525155274
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae80610aff09e00002334d7",
      "text": "  主要メンバーの信頼を下げる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155344,
      "updated": 1525155349
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae805caaff09e00002334d3",
      "text": " 2: 嘘を付く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155274,
      "updated": 1525155302
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae805cfaff09e00002334d4",
      "text": " \t平気で繰り返し嘘をつく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155279,
      "updated": 1525155310
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae805ffaff09e00002334d6",
      "text": "  本当のことを言う人の信頼を下げる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155328,
      "updated": 1525155353
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae805f6aff09e00002334d5",
      "text": "　3: 重要人物に媚びる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155318,
      "updated": 1525155366
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae80626aff09e00002334d9",
      "text": " \tポジティブなバイアスを作っておく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155367,
      "updated": 1525155479
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae80696aff09e00002334dc",
      "text": "  これによって、クラッシャーを排斥する動きが起きた時に「対等な喧嘩」と誤認する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155479,
      "updated": 1525155510
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae806b6aff09e00002334dd",
      "text": "\t4: 群れる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155510,
      "updated": 1525155539
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae806d2aff09e00002334de",
      "text": " \t弱気な人を子分にする。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155539,
      "updated": 1525155567
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae806d3aff09e00002334df",
      "text": "  意見を言うときに「私だけじゃない」と主張できるようになる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155539,
      "updated": 1525155587
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae80703aff09e00002334e1",
      "text": "\t5: アンタッチャブルな雰囲気を作ること",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155587,
      "updated": 1525155640
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae80738aff09e00002334e4",
      "text": " \t感情的になるなどの振る舞いを見せる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155640,
      "updated": 1525155709
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae8077daff09e00002334e6",
      "text": "  周囲の人が懸念をいだいても、関わり合いになるのが面倒なので指摘しない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155709,
      "updated": 1525155723
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae8078daff09e00002334e8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155725,
      "updated": 1525155725
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae80708aff09e00002334e3",
      "text": "対策",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155592,
      "updated": 1525155767
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae807b7aff09e00002334ea",
      "text": "\t事実を収集する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155767,
      "updated": 1525155771
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae807baaff09e00002334eb",
      "text": " 重要人物を含んだ大勢の人がいる場で糾弾する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525155771,
      "updated": 1525155778
    }
  ]
}